We have recommended and the Municipal Mayor agreed to direct the:
Bids and Award Committee to submit the Purchase Order/Contract Agreement with all the complete bidding document within five (5) working days upon perfection as provided in the COA Circular No. 2009-001, and;
Accounting Office to ensure that all the necessary documentary required under COA Circular 2012-001 for the completeness and legality of the claims for the payment of procurement are attached.

